#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing.rst:None
msgid "View of the blank campaign form in Odoo Email Marketing."
msgstr "Hình ảnh biểu mẫu chiến dịch trống trong Odoo Email Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing.rst:754
msgid ""
"From this campaign form, a :guilabel:`Campaign Name`, "
